oracle.pg.common

Class ColumnToAttrMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.pg.common.ColumnToAttrMapping

  • public class ColumnToAttrMapping
extends java.lang.Object
    A class denoting the mappings between a CSV File or RDBMS Table column name and an attribute name. This class is used to specify the mapping and data type for the K/V pairs generation in the CSV2OPG and RDBMS2OPG converters.
